To compile the code:
1. Make sure you have gradle installed
2. Run gradle jar (on Unix) or gradlew jar (on Windows)
3. The jar file at build/libs/nlp-homework2.jar from your current directory

To run the program (assuming you are in the same directory as the jar file):
java -jar nlp-homework2.jar -f <corpus.txt-path> -s1 <content of sentence 1> -s2 <content of sentence 2>